OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781197569
OL,3,CSmall boat pilots first to be
OL,4,Csentenced for endangering others in
OL,5,CChannel
OL,7,FTwo small boat pilots are the first to
OL,8,Fbe facing sentence under a new offence
OL,9,Fof endangering others during a Channel
OL,10,Fcrossing.
OL,12,FAfghan national Tajik Mohammad and
OL,13,FSudanese national Alnour Ali will both
OL,14,Fappear at Canterbury Crown Court on
OL,15,FWednesday over two separate dangerous
OL,16,Fjourneys.
OL,18,FEndangering others during a journey by
OL,19,Fsea to the UK is a new offence that
OL,20,Fcame into force in January as part of
OL,21,Fnew border security legislation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
