FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781197569
OL,3,CSmall boat pilots first to be
OL,4,Csentenced for endangering others in
OL,5,CChannel
OL,7,FUnder the offence, those who endanger
OL,8,For risk another life at sea could face
OL,9,Fup to five years in prison, or up to
OL,10,Fsix years if they are in breach of a
OL,11,Fdeportation order.
OL,13,FMohammad was the first to be convicted
OL,14,Funder the new law having pleaded
OL,15,Fguilty at Canterbury Crown Court on
OL,16,FApril 21.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
