PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781197569
OL,3,CSmall boat pilots first to be
OL,4,Csentenced for endangering others in
OL,5,CChannel
OL,7,FAccording to the Crown Prosecution
OL,8,FService (CPS), the 32-year-old
OL,9,Fabandoned the dinghy he was driving
OL,10,Facross the English Channel and its
OL,11,Fpassengers when a rescue ship arrived
OL,12,Fon January 17.
OL,14,FThe boat was overcrowded and some
OL,15,Fpassengers were not wearing life
OL,16,Fjackets during the attempted crossing
OL,17,Fin poor weather conditions, the CPS
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
