PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781197569
OL,3,CSmall boat pilots first to be
OL,4,Csentenced for endangering others in
OL,5,CChannel
OL,7,FElsewhere, Ali admitted the charge of
OL,8,Fendangering others during a sea
OL,9,Fcrossing on April 9 at the same court
OL,10,Flast month.
OL,12,FThat day two men and two women drowned
OL,13,Fafter being swept away by strong
OL,14,Fcurrents while trying to climb on to a
OL,15,Fdinghy at Equihen-Plage, near Boulogne-
OL,16,Fsur-Mer in France.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
