PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781197569
OL,3,CSmall boat pilots first to be
OL,4,Csentenced for endangering others in
OL,5,CChannel
OL,7,FFollowing his conviction, National
OL,8,FCrime Agency branch operations manager
OL,9,FEmma Brown said: "Working with
OL,10,Fcolleagues at home and abroad, we are
OL,11,Fdetermined to do all we can to
OL,12,Fidentify and bring to justice those
OL,13,Fresponsible for small boat crossings.
OL,15,F"The tragic deaths illustrate again
OL,16,Fhow perilous these crossings are and
OL,17,Fthe callous nature of the criminals
OL,18,Forganising them."
OL,26,@qD@ROUwD@AOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
