PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781197569
OL,3,CSmall boat pilots first to be
OL,4,Csentenced for endangering others in
OL,5,CChannel
OL,7,FAccording to the Home Office, the
OL,8,Foffence is designed to stop more
OL,9,Fpeople being crammed into unsafe boats
OL,10,Fand would apply to those involved in
OL,11,Fphysical aggression and intimidation,
OL,12,Fas well as anyone who resists rescue.
OL,14,FThe new charge includes physical or
OL,15,Fpsychological injury and covers
OL,16,Fjourneys by water to the UK from
OL,17,FFrance, Belgium and the Netherlands.
OL,19,FThe sentencing hearings for Mohammad
OL,20,Fand Ali will begin at 10am on
OL,21,FWednesday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
